{"tid":2241914,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"1932年嘅小說，代入2020年中國，毫無違和感。","createTime":"2020-10-13T15:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T09:05:56.000Z","uid":113155,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6c843a4f446f2afbe4b8e8473e4f9baf2a2ced1e","tid":2241914,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"老舍《貓城記》<br />\n1932中共仲未成立，點解我感覺本書講緊而家嘅中共，入邊啲人都係而家嘅中國人。<br />\n<br />\n文豪就係文豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌，中國真係古國，一百年不變、一千年不變都似。"},{"pid":"84a50aa801fd3ae6165f6e131b50c53faa5669a6","tid":2241914,"uid":196924,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨 1921年就成立"},{"pid":"e6fc91e2c7aa47d6653a14864d7fe106e9e2227c","tid":2241914,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:45:55.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6737f7aa61bd3ee61601ef208825afcf7824512e","tid":2241914,"uid":303495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:46:18.000Z","msg":"你睇吓佢點死"},{"pid":"a7c2a6f6b657521a7d1b53e8ef67954341fb2831","tid":2241914,"uid":71708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5ab3401ee1c16251b00214dcaa183c4a71f21e","tid":2241914,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"84a50aa801fd3ae6165f6e131b50c53faa5669a6","tid":2241914,"uid":196924,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨 1921年就成立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"Sor 非歷史撚，漏咗哩個。<br />\n我理解內容似寫清朝民國mix，但完全同中共而家所作所為樣。"},{"pid":"bc2d18ea07e77c551196f7d331e06b080b3b11f5","tid":2241914,"uid":300387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"老舍畀中國人批鬥死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d8ab0f87e3a7578cce53718807bb10c1f84460","tid":2241914,"uid":113155,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6737f7aa61bd3ee61601ef208825afcf7824512e","tid":2241914,"uid":303495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:46:18.000Z","msg":"你睇吓佢點死"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:03:15.000Z","msg":"未睇完，睇到七成到，覺得好悲哀。<br />\n淨係做表面功夫，內裏無論政府定人民都同一百年前一q樣，無進步過。<br />\n真係好想睇下哩個國家冇咗獨裁統治，會點發展。"},{"pid":"fcdc34e3156b0f68ca23b145f2555523a033b4c6","tid":2241914,"uid":113155,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bc2d18ea07e77c551196f7d331e06b080b3b11f5","tid":2241914,"uid":300387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"老舍畀中國人批鬥死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"佢寫啲咁到肉嘅嘢，唔出奇。<br />\n即使非文革，放喺而家，佢一喺去台灣或毆美，一喺被自殺。<br />\n哎，好慘。<br />\n來生不做中國人。"},{"pid":"5f836bc90cd94b64b9c21ea87a7915ea035d0004","tid":2241914,"uid":113155,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"6737f7aa61bd3ee61601ef208825afcf7824512e","tid":2241914,"uid":303495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:46:18.000Z","msg":"你睇吓佢點死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"喔，你講老舍。<br />\n其實唔洗睇都估到。"},{"pid":"921dccc384ae17e60cebd1a4e8810e32b1a159e3","tid":2241914,"uid":274161,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T22:01:15.000Z","msg":"知唔知中國好多人叫呢個時代做 後清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1544346bc7c673ab5158daea50a848b6fe9af05","tid":2241914,"uid":274161,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"fcdc34e3156b0f68ca23b145f2555523a033b4c6","tid":2241914,"uid":113155,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bc2d18ea07e77c551196f7d331e06b080b3b11f5","tid":2241914,"uid":300387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"老舍畀中國人批鬥死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"佢寫啲咁到肉嘅嘢，唔出奇。<br />\n即使非文革，放喺而家，佢一喺去台灣或毆美，一喺被自殺。<br />\n哎，好慘。<br />\n來生不做中國人。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T22:07:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢49之後都寫過好多歌德文章<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/老舍#1949年後的創作\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E8%80%81%E8%88%8D%231949%E5%B9%B4%E5%BE%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=af11ec24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/老舍#1949年後的創作</a><br />\n佢可能係恁唔明點解自己咁忠心都會被批鬥<br />\n特別係文人被虐打，點頂得順<br />\n<blockquote>23日下午，北京女八中（現北京市魯迅中學）紅衛兵衝擊北京市文聯，老舍與30多位作家、藝術家一道被掛上「走資派」、「牛鬼蛇神」、「反動文人」牌子，押至北京孔廟大成門前，被押着向焚毀京劇服裝、道具的大火下跪，慘遭侮辱、毒打。血流滿面、遍體鱗傷的老舍被押回北京市文聯，又因還手「對抗紅衛兵」而被加掛「現行反革命」牌子，遭到紅衛兵變本加厲的殘酷毆打，隨後被北京市文聯革委會副主任浩然送到西長安街派出所，直至8月24日凌晨回到家中；而紅衛兵組織亦要求他24日上午到北京市文聯繼續接受批鬥。8月24日清晨，傷心之至的老舍獨自離家出走到北京城西北角外的太平湖畔；穿着白襯衫藍褲子，拿着《毛澤東詩詞》在岸念了整整一天，又坐了大半夜。當日深夜，老舍於太平湖畔跳湖自盡，終年67歲。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c39cc2c906e4de67aa5f2929c6827f7f841cc123","tid":2241914,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T22:43:12.000Z","msg":"《貓城記》睇簡介似講緊内鬥？<br />\n1932年寫，係未受31年918刺激？"},{"pid":"ec4e46f28ca591b9cb878068c17791e76cc051d8","tid":2241914,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c39cc2c906e4de67aa5f2929c6827f7f841cc123","tid":2241914,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T22:43:12.000Z","msg":"《貓城記》睇簡介似講緊内鬥？<br />\n1932年寫，係未受31年918刺激？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T23:15:26.000Z","msg":"未睇完，打風唔洗番工係咁2睇下，冇深究，又唔似講內鬥喎。<br />\n講當時嘅政治、人民、教育。"},{"pid":"89e3b02290eeb32c769ed36b69388b4c84a34ac0","tid":2241914,"uid":317906,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"08d8ab0f87e3a7578cce53718807bb10c1f84460","tid"